---
import { AppConfig } from "../../data";
---

<section class="Slide">
    <div class="container-fluid">
        <div class="header">
            <h2 class="title">Go-to-Market Roadmap</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Four phases to turn { AppConfig.brand_name } from a well-positioned new company into the default growth technology partner for ambitious businesses across East Africa.</p>
            <ol class="grid-ol grid-rows">
                <li>
                    <span>01. Brand Foundation (Months 1–2)</span>
                    <span>Lock the brand strategy. Build the visual identity. Launch the website with outcome-focused copy and a case study foundation. Define the content voice and publish the first social proof.</span>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <span>02. Authority Building (Months 3–5)</span>
                    <span>Publish 3–5 case studies with specific, measurable outcomes. Launch a weekly LinkedIn content strategy. Speak at 2+ Nairobi SME and startup events. Build organic SEO foundation around growth-focused search terms.</span>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <span>03. Channel Expansion (Months 6–9)</span>
                    <span>Launch a structured referral programme. Form partnerships with business incubators and accelerators. Test paid digital with tight audience targeting. Introduce retainer packages for ongoing growth support.</span>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <span>04. Scale & Expand (Month 10+)</span>
                    <span>Productise recurring services. Build a client success playbook. Expand to Uganda, Tanzania, and Rwanda with the proven Nairobi model. Begin hiring to match demand without compromising output quality.</span>
                </li>
            </ol>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
